description:
(STR+10 WIS+20 SPD+10) When an ally is below 40% HP the wielder 
gains SPD+50%.
name: Emergency Staff
note:
<Passive State: 20>
<Custom Passive Condition>
condition = false;
for (var i = 0; i < $gameParty.aliveMembers().length; ++i) {
  var member = $gameParty.aliveMembers()[i];
  if (!member) continue;
  if (member === user) continue;
  if (member.hpRate() <= 0.4) condition = true;
}
</Custom Passive Condition>

description: Gain more power with each passing turn in combat.
name: Rod of Ages
note:
<Custom Parameters>
if ($gameParty.inBattle()) {
  var turns = user.turnCount();
  var charges = Math.floor(turns / 2);
  maxhp = 20 * charges;
  maxmp = 40 * charges;
  mat = 4 * charges;
}
</Custom Parameters>

description:
Gain more power with each passing turn in combat.
(Capped to a 10 turn Buff)
name: Rod of Sages
note:
<Custom Parameters>
if ($gameParty.inBattle()) {
  var turns = user.turnCount();
  var charges = Math.floor(turns / 2);
  charges = Math.min(charges, 10);
  maxhp = 20 * charges;
  maxmp = 40 * charges;
  mat = 4 * charges;
}
</Custom Parameters>
